                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17881022-66-off299 t17881022-66-cd300"></join> last, one pair of leather shoes, value 6 s. a pair<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178810220085"></xptr>of sattin breeches, value 14 s. a silk waistcoat, value 5 s. a worsted waistcoat, value 3 s. a pair of silver shoe buckles, value 7 s. a pair of plated ditto, value 8 d. one cork screw, value 3 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17881022-66-victim564" type="victimName">
