               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>LITTON, <rs id="t17881022-66-verdict305" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17881022-66-verdict305" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>To be <rs id="t17881022-66-punish306" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17881022-66-punish306" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17881022-66-punish306" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="whipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17881022-66-defend562 t17881022-66-punish306"></join>
               severely whipped
            </rs> and passed to his settlement at Bristol.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
